[HEADING=2][CENTER][FONT=verdana]S Pen Information[/FONT][/CENTER][/HEADING]
[CENTER][FONT=verdana][B]⚠️ S Pen Changes in S25 Ultra:[/B]

The built-in S Pen is now [B]passive[/B] (no Bluetooth).

[B]What works:[/B]
✅ Writing, drawing, hovering, pressure sensitivity
✅ Selection gestures, screen-off memo

[B]What's removed:[/B]
❌ Air Actions (remote shutter, gesture controls)
❌ Remote presentation control

[B]Solution:[/B] Purchase the separate [URL='https://www.samsung.com/s-pen-pro']S Pen Pro[/URL] (~$100) for Bluetooth features.
It charges via USB-C but does NOT fit in the phone's silo.[/FONT][/CENTER]

